#. Tag: title
#: locate.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locate &GUI; Frontend"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: primary
#: locate.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locate"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:12
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; has a &GUI; front end for the <command>locate</command> command "
"(findutils). Locate is used for fast file searching not from a folder but a "
"database. The package contains among other files, <command>locate</command> "
"and <command>updatedb</command>. <command>updatedb</command> goes through "
"the local file system and stores the file entries in the database. "
"<command>cron</command> often calls <command>updatedb</command> every night "
"(set with <application>KCron</application>). Choose <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Locate...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> to "
"start this feature. <link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Konfigurator</link> "
"can set additional arguments for <command>updatedb</command>."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; a&GUI; eest lõpp tingimusel<command></command> käsk on tingimusel "
"kiire fail otsimine mitte   a a andmebaas pakett sisaldab kaks "
"failid<command></command> ja<command></command> kuni kohalik fail süsteem ja "
"fail asukohas andmebaas<command> cron</command> sageli<command></command> "
"järgnevaga Vali<emphasis role=\"bold\"><menuchoice><guimenu> Tööriistad</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem></guimenuitem></menuchoice></emphasis> või<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap> Backspace</keycap><keycap> L</keycap></"
"keycombo> kuni start<link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\"></link> arguments "
"tingimusel<command></command>."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:32
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Checkbox Options"
msgstr "Märkekast Valikud"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:35
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show only the existing files</guilabel>: if the database contains "
"entries which no longer exist any more (deleted, moved since the last "
"<command>updatedb</command>), <command>locate</command> does not list them. "
"It checks the existence of each file before the listing in the results "
"window (slow)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel> Näita failid</guilabel> kui andmebaas sisaldab ei iga rohkem "
"kustutatud<command></command><command></command> mitte list  /  fail "
"asukohas aken aeglane."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:45
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Case Sensitive</guilabel>: unchecking it allows lower and upper "
"case search."
msgstr "<guilabel></guilabel> tahaplaanile saatmine ja otsing."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:50
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Action buttons"
msgstr "Toiming"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:53
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Locate</guibutton>: executes <command>locate <replaceable>foo "
"foo</replaceable></command> and places its output into the results window."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton></guibutton><command><replaceable> foo foo</replaceable></"
"command> ja väljund aken."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:60
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Stop</guibutton>: stops the locating process."
msgstr "<guibutton> Peata</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:65
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>UpdateDB</guibutton>: starts <command>updatedb</command> for "
"updating the locate database after entering the root password."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton></guibutton><command></command> tingimusel uuendamine andmebaas "
"juur parool."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:71
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Close</guibutton>: closes the locate window."
msgstr "<guibutton> Sulge</guibutton> aken."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:76
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Results window"
msgstr "Tulemused aken"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:79
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click on an item: steps to its folder, makes the item visible and "
"closes the locate dialog."
msgstr "Topelt sees kuni nähtav ja."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:83
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Right click: edits/views/finds the menu."
msgstr "Paremal vaated menüü."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:86
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F3</keycap>: views the current item."
msgstr "<keycap> F3</keycap> vaated aktiivne."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:90
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F4</keycap>: edits the current item."
msgstr "<keycap> F4</keycap> aktiivne."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:94
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>: finds files "
"in the results window."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap></keycap></keycombo> failid "
"asukohas aken."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:100
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>: shows the "
"next search result."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap></keycap></keycombo> järgmine "
"otsing."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:106
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>: shows the "
"previous search result."
msgstr "<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap></keycap></keycombo> otsing."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:114
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The results window supports dragging items to other windows and copy to "
"clipboard (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"aken elemendid kuni muu ja koopiaõigus kuni lõikepuhver<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap></keycap></keycombo>."
